title: Radiant Radiology Patient
description:
The Radiant Radiology Patient app is used by patients to securely access the results of their radiology scans performed at Radiant Radiology.

The app will allow you to view and easily share your results with other health professionals. Once your results are ready to view, you will receive a text message containing a web link. You will need this link to activate your account and set a secure password.

For help and other information go to radiant.zed.link

Please Note: Your doctor will be able to access your images and reports as soon as they are available. You should always return to your doctor to discuss your result.
